00:41:17,111 --> 00:41:19,612
I didn't think so.

924
00:41:19,614 --> 00:41:22,114
This is Detective Bell
from the NYPD.

925
00:41:22,116 --> 00:41:24,283
I told him about
the world's worst dry cleaner's,

