00:41:24,285 --> 00:41:25,484
and he got curious.

927
00:41:25,486 --> 00:41:26,819
BELL:
Do you know who bought

928
00:41:26,821 --> 00:41:28,337
this place from
the Korean couple

929
00:41:28,339 --> 00:41:30,506
who used to own it?
It's a shell company.

930
00:41:30,508 --> 00:41:32,124
I can't even pronounce it,

931
00:41:32,126 --> 00:41:34,794
but my friends at the NYPD
know all about it.

932
00:41:34,796 --> 00:41:36,429
They think it's
linked to smuggling,

933
00:41:36,431 --> 00:41:38,514
human trafficking...
other fun stuff.

934
00:41:38,516 --> 00:41:40,933
So now I know why you're
so terrible at dry cleaning.

935
00:41:40,935 --> 00:41:43,052
Because the only thing
your owners want you to clean

936
00:41:43,054 --> 00:41:44,770
is their money.

